                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Ingesting an extradimensional space like that found in a <em>bag of holding</em> deals [[/r 12d8 #force]] force damage to the slithering rift and its occupants.</p>\n<p>The slithering rift then immediately uses Out You Go.</p>"
